g", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741772-end-of-an-era-what-gelsinger-departure-means-for-intel", "pub_date": "2024-12-03 19:06:08"}, {"id": "4741548", "title": "2025: Seeing Some Crazy Things For Gold And The Stock Market", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1336046534/image_1336046534.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Yelling man and falling graphs\" data-id=\"1336046534\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"996px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1336046534/image_1336046534.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1336046534/image_1336046534.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1336046534/image_1336046534.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1336046534/image_1336046534.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1336046534/image_1336046534.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1336046534/image_1336046534.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1336046534/image_1336046534.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1336046534/image_1336046534.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">ismagilov/iStock via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>I was recently honored to be a featured speaker, as well as a gold market panelist, at the 50<sup>th</sup> anniversary of the New Orleans Investment Conference. So, what follows is a slightly modified version of the presentation I gave during my</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1336046534/image_1336046534.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741548-2025-seeing-some-crazy-things-for-gold-and-the-stock-market", "pub_date": "2024-12-03 19:00:00"}, {"id": "4741770", "title": "Tesla Faces An Uphill Battle In 2025", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2124191987/image_2124191987.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"A Tesla Cybertruck in a parking spot in Irvine, California\" data-id=\"2124191987\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2124191987/image_2124191987.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2124191987/image_2124191987.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2124191987/image_2124191987.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2124191987/image_2124191987.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2124191987/image_2124191987.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2124191987/image_2124191987.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2124191987/image_2124191987.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2124191987/image_2124191987.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">Sven Piper</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><b>Tesla,